(143, 'litespeed.cloud._summary', '{\"curr_request.wp\\/ver\":0,\"last_request.wp\\/ver\":1633109119,\"news.utime\":1633109076,\"curr_request.wp\\/news\":0,\"last_request.wp\\/news\":1633109076,\"news.id\":15,\"news.plugin\":\"\",\"news.title\":\"LiteSpeed Cache Plugin\",\"news.content\":\"<h2>Version 3.5.1 is now available.<\\/h2>\\n\\n<p>This version includes significant changes to JavaScript optimization. <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/github.com\\/litespeedtech\\/lscache_wp\\/blob\\/f17ca7bc5e47761cc1b1ca499d1e7a8f41a3d0a4\\/readme.txt#L250-L263\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">See release log here<\\/a><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>Due to these changes, the <code>JS Combine<\\/code> and <code>Load JS Deferred<\\/code> functions will be turned OFF. Please turn them back on and verify that your site still works properly.<\\/p>\\n\\n<p>Also, <code>jQuery<\\/code> will be automatically excluded by default. If you have no problems with JQuery, you may remove it from the <code>JS Excludes<\\/code> setting.<\\/p>\\n\\n<p>\\n\\tTo install v3.5.1:\\n\\t<ul style=\\\"list-style-type:\'- \';\\\">\\n\\t\\t<li> Navigate to <b>Toolbox > Beta Test<\\/b>.<\\/li>\\n\\t\\t<li> Type <code>https:\\/\\/github.com\\/litespeedtech\\/lscache_wp\\/commit\\/e0c7c26d81ef3fabcc1936491667b71fc5d13463<\\/code> in the input field.<\\/li>\\n\\t\\t<li> Press the <b>Upgrade<\\/b> button.<\\/li>\\n\\t<\\/ul>\\n<p>\\n\\n\\n<p>\\n\\t<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wordpress.org\\/support\\/topic\\/v3-5-1-is-ready-%f0%9f%8e%8a\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Learn more about this v3.5.1 upgrade.<\\/a>\\n<\\/p>\\n\\n\\n<p>\\n\\tIf you encounter any problems, you may revert to the previous version <b>v3.4.2<\\/b>:\\n\\t<ul style=\\\"list-style-type:\'- \';\\\">\\n\\t\\t<li>Navigate to <b>Toolbox > Beta Test<\\/b>.<\\/li>\\n\\t\\t<li>Select the previous stable version from the drop down.<\\/li>\\n\\t\\t<li>Press the <b>Upgrade<\\/b> button.<\\/li>\\n\\t<\\/ul>\\n<\\/p>\\n\\n<p>Please send us feedback, especially if you have problems, via our <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.litespeedtech.com\\/slack\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Slack<\\/a> -> <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/golitespeed.slack.com\\/archives\\/C3RJHNBTQ\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">#wpcache channel<\\/a>.<\\/p>\\n\\n<br>\\nThank you!<br>\\nThe LiteSpeed Team\\n\",\"news.zip\":\"https:\\/\\/api.quic.cloud\\/wp\\/zip\\/e0c7c26d81ef3fabcc1936491667b71fc5d13463.zip\",\"news.new\":1,\"curr_request.ver\":0,\"last_request.ver\":1633109843}', 'yes'),
