(682, 121, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"ffe2e16\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"layout\":\"full_width\",\"margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"45\",\"right\":0,\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":0,\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"b305d94\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"15035e5\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"Forr\\u00f3fiando\",\"align\":\"center\",\"title_color\":\"#502025\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Russo One\",\"typography_font_size\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":45,\"sizes\":[]},\"typography_font_weight\":\"300\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"c3ab7f0\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"20\",\"margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"45\",\"right\":0,\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":0,\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"13b3758\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null,\"content_position\":\"center\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"5af6c1b\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/cirandeira.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020\\/10\\/Copia-de-Logo-1.jpg\",\"id\":72}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"908e268\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null,\"content_position\":\"center\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"f2705f6\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Trazer Hist\\u00f3rias sobre a nossa cultura entremeadas por muita m\\u00fasica e informa\\u00e7\\u00e3o. Assim \\u00e9 o projeto \\u201cForrofiando uma Hist\\u00f3ria\\u201d. Focado nas tradi\\u00e7\\u00f5es da m\\u00fasica nordestina, o cancioneiro popular sempre nos traz um retrato dos costumes, modos de pensar, agir e tamb\\u00e9m representa muitas vezes, um grito sufocado de quem n\\u00e3o tem como pedir ajuda.\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0Sempre com um roteiro estudado e pensado de forma a construir um novelo hist\\u00f3rico, o \\u201dForrofiando uma Hist\\u00f3ria\\u201d \\u00e9 uma divertida maneira de trazer conhecimento com ludicidade, pois a m\\u00fasica nordestina, mesmo com mensagens tristes, tem no seu \\u00edntimo, muita riqueza e alegria.\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"align\":\"center\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"09ea240\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"49c3664\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"89686f6\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"HIST\\u00d3RICO\",\"align\":\"center\",\"title_color\":\"#502025\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Russo One\",\"typography_font_size\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":35,\"sizes\":[]},\"typography_font_weight\":\"300\",\"header_size\":\"h3\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"},{\"id\":\"2d9619b\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"bb9fa77\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"c250b13\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">A primeira vers\\u00e3o do projeto foi em homenagem\\u00a0 ao dia nacional do forr\\u00f3 em 13 de dezembro de 2018 no SESC Nogueira. Dia de nascimento de Luiz Gonzaga. Depois veio o dia do nordestino, 8 de outubro, na Casa de Cultura Cl\\u00e1udio de Souza, com muitas hist\\u00f3rias sobre os nordestinos e sua saga mundo afora. Ainda em 2019, comemorou-se novamente o dia nacional do forr\\u00f3 e tamb\\u00e9m uma homenagem ao samba, o \\u201cForrofiando uma Hist\\u00f3ria - Esse forr\\u00f3 d\\u00e1 samba\\u201d, contando a rela\\u00e7\\u00e3o entre os cantadores de embolada e coco, com o samba no Rio de Janeiro.<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"align\":\"center\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":true}],\"isInner\":true}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"52a90a4\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"45\",\"right\":0,\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":0,\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"3ec1a29\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"8ebd2bc\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"QUEM SOMOS\\n\",\"align\":\"center\",\"title_color\":\"#502025\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Russo One\",\"typography_font_size\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":35,\"sizes\":[]},\"typography_font_weight\":\"300\",\"header_size\":\"h3\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"},{\"id\":\"77826f8\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"95458cd\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"7c40ed3\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">\\u00a0O projeto \\u201cForrofiando uma Hist\\u00f3ria\\u201d \\u00e9 uma idealiza\\u00e7\\u00e3o da Tarrabufado Cultural e nasceu da necessidade de informar e trazer conhecimento \\u00e0 popula\\u00e7\\u00e3o, de maneira l\\u00fadica e divertida. As apresenta\\u00e7\\u00f5es ficam \\u00e0 cargo de Guilherme Mar\\u00e1 que junto com Mirele Maravilhas, realizam todo o trabalho de elabora\\u00e7\\u00e3o de textos e roteiros para cada apresenta\\u00e7\\u00e3o.\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"align\":\"center\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":true}],\"isInner\":true}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"26a42c9\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"45\",\"right\":0,\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":0,\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"68785eb\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"f8c6d76\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"FUTURO\\n\",\"align\":\"center\",\"title_color\":\"#502025\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Russo One\",\"typography_font_size\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":35,\"sizes\":[]},\"typography_font_weight\":\"300\",\"header_size\":\"h3\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"},{\"id\":\"7d5881d\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"76155fe\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"3183da7\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Por conta do momento atual devido \\u00e0 pandemia, as apresenta\\u00e7\\u00f5es em p\\u00fablico est\\u00e3o suspensas, mas a vontade de realizar nunca termina. Portanto, o projeto Forrofiando uma Hist\\u00f3ria, adaptando-se \\u00e0s novas tecnologias de comunica\\u00e7\\u00e3o on-line, j\\u00e1 se programou e estruturou quatro lindas apresenta\\u00e7\\u00f5es para o ano de 2020.<\\/span><\\/p><p>\\u00a0<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">NOVOS PROJETOS<\\/span><\\/p><ul><li style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0S\\u00e3o Jo\\u00e3o na Rede;<\\/span><\\/li><li style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0Semana da Cultura Nordestina;<\\/span><\\/li><li style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0Dia do Nordestino;<\\/span><\\/li><li style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0Dia Nacional do Forr\\u00f3.<\\/span><\\/li><\\/ul><p>\\u00a0<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">S\\u00c3O JO\\u00c3O NA REDE<\\/span><\\/p><p>\\u00a0<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">SEMANA DA CULTURA NORDESTINA<\\/span><\\/p><p>\\u00a0<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">DIA DO NORDESTINO<\\/span><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0Dia 08 de Outubro \\u00e9 a data que se comemora o dia do nordestino. Essa data marca o nascimento de, talvez, o maior poeta popular sertanejo, o cearense Patativa do Assar\\u00e9. Um dia de comemorar, reverenciar os mestres e tamb\\u00e9m refletir sobre como o nordestino se espalhou pelo mundo afora e ainda encontrando preconceito, se supera a cada dia. Contos e causos regado a muito forr\\u00f3 p\\u00e9-de-serra.<\\/span><\\/p><p>\\u00a0<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">DIA NACIONAL DO FORR\\u00d3<\\/span><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0A saga de um menino pobre, que cantou e musicou a alma do nordestino e se tornou representante de toda essa na\\u00e7\\u00e3o. A hist\\u00f3ria de Luiz Gonzaga, de menino \\u00e0 Rei do Bai\\u00e3o. Reverenciado no mundo inteiro, sua poesia e sua m\\u00fasica se eternizaram ao longo de mais de quarenta anos de carreira. N\\u00e3o poderia haver outra data mais importante para o Dia Nacional do Forr\\u00f3, que 13 de dezembro, dia de nascimento de mestre Lua Gonzaga.<\\/span><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0No formato de trio p\\u00e9-de-serra, Guilherme Mar\\u00e1 vai trazendo curiosidades e fatos que marcaram a vida de Gonzag\\u00e3o entremeados pela sua incr\\u00edvel m\\u00fasica. Viva o dia nacional do Forr\\u00f3!<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"align\":\"left\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":true}],\"isInner\":true}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
