(898, 173, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"f8d96ce\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"layout\":\"full_width\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"b3bc7ca\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"39c30b6\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"slides\":[{\"heading\":\"Cirandeira Cuntural\",\"description\":\"\",\"button_text\":\"Sobre\",\"background_color\":\"#833CA300\",\"_id\":\"3e83b9b\",\"background_image\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/cirandeira.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020\\/10\\/Guilherme-Mara-5.-Mariana-Kreishner.jpg\",\"id\":45},\"background_ken_burns\":\"yes\",\"background_overlay\":\"yes\"},{\"heading\":\"Confira todos os nossos Projetos\",\"description\":\"\",\"button_text\":\"Clique Aqui\",\"background_color\":\"#833CA300\",\"background_image\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/cirandeira.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020\\/10\\/DSC_1781.jpg\",\"id\":48},\"background_ken_burns\":\"yes\",\"background_overlay\":\"yes\",\"_id\":\"ca5604d\"},{\"heading\":\"Entre em Contato\",\"description\":\"\",\"button_text\":\"Clique Aqui\",\"background_color\":\"#833CA300\",\"background_image\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/cirandeira.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020\\/10\\/DSC_3032.jpg\",\"id\":50},\"background_ken_burns\":\"yes\",\"background_overlay\":\"yes\",\"_id\":\"616798a\"}],\"slides_height\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":488,\"sizes\":[]}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"slides\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"bddd7c1\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"20\",\"margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"45\",\"right\":0,\"bottom\":\"45\",\"left\":0,\"isLinked\":true}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"9586cbb\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null,\"animation\":\"fadeInLeft\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"1fa2482\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/cirandeira.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020\\/10\\/Mirele-e-Mara-Casa-de-reboco-Parque-Asa-Branca-EXU-PE.jpg\",\"id\":15},\"image_border_border\":\"solid\",\"image_border_color\":\"#62363B\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"9e549b4\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null,\"content_position\":\"center\",\"animation\":\"fadeInRight\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"b2b0711\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Por ser um pa\\u00eds de propor\\u00e7\\u00f5es continentais, o Brasil revela-se como um dos maiores celeiros culturais do mundo, onde a diversidade comp\\u00f5e essa aquarela de cores, m\\u00fasicas, manifesta\\u00e7\\u00f5es religiosas, pratos t\\u00edpicos, express\\u00f5es teatrais, express\\u00f5es visuais, vestimentas entre diversos outros aspectos que definem a cultura de um povo.<\\/span><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0Valorizar nossos mestres, reverenciar os anci\\u00e3os\\u00a0 e incentivar os\\u00a0 novos talentos \\u00e9 sempre um desafio para os educadores e agentes culturais. Dessa maneira atua o Tarrabufado Cultural, atrav\\u00e9s de pesquisas e da realiza\\u00e7\\u00e3o de projetos focados na cultura, informa\\u00e7\\u00e3o, capacita\\u00e7\\u00e3o, forma\\u00e7\\u00e3o de plat\\u00e9ia e entretenimento para a popula\\u00e7\\u00e3o.<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"align\":\"center\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"0bdfdc0\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"45\",\"right\":0,\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":0,\"isLinked\":false},\"_element_id\":\"objetivo\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"e78c44c\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"b49b36b\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"Objetivo\",\"align\":\"center\",\"title_color\":\"#502025\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Russo One\",\"typography_font_size\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":45,\"sizes\":[]},\"typography_font_weight\":\"300\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"},{\"id\":\"bcb6401\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"20\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"031596b\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null,\"animation\":\"fadeInLeft\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"c884dd6\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Com o mundo cada vez mais din\\u00e2mico, e atualmente, enfrentando uma crise sanit\\u00e1ria e econ\\u00f4mica sem precedentes, a Cirandeira Cultural, busca agregar os valores culturais, alinhados ao bem-estar e a uma consci\\u00eancia mais humanit\\u00e1ria.\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0Pontuar a informa\\u00e7\\u00e3o como base essencial na forma\\u00e7\\u00e3o de cada indiv\\u00edduo. N\\u00e3o somente o entretenimento pela divers\\u00e3o, mas sim pela evolu\\u00e7\\u00e3o como seres humanos.\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0Difundir a cultura em locais de poucos recursos e buscar favorecer um pensamento autocr\\u00edtico de cada indiv\\u00edduo.<\\/span><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0Valorizar em vida, os mestres e reconhec\\u00ea-los como agentes que transformaram seu meio e muito contribu\\u00edram\\/contribuem com a nossa cultura.<\\/span><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0Criar ferramentas e solu\\u00e7\\u00f5es de aprendizado e est\\u00edmulos para as crian\\u00e7as, adolescentes e todos os novos talentos que precisem de orienta\\u00e7\\u00f5es.<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"align\":\"center\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":true},{\"id\":\"67b3f96\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null,\"animation\":\"fadeInRight\",\"content_position\":\"center\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"16dddb4\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/cirandeira.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020\\/10\\/Copia-de-DSC_6897.jpg\",\"id\":59},\"image_border_border\":\"solid\",\"image_border_color\":\"#62363B\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":true}],\"isInner\":true}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"42ab1b6\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"45\",\"right\":0,\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":0,\"isLinked\":false},\"_element_id\":\"quem-somos\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"16c6771\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"78dac05\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"Quem Somos\",\"align\":\"center\",\"title_color\":\"#502025\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Russo One\",\"typography_font_size\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":45,\"sizes\":[]},\"typography_font_weight\":\"300\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"},{\"id\":\"eaaec50\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"20\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"0dde63b\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null,\"animation\":\"fadeInLeft\",\"content_position\":\"center\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"87a5e80\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/cirandeira.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020\\/10\\/Mirele-Maravilhas-e-Guilherme-Mara.jpeg\",\"id\":62},\"image_border_border\":\"solid\",\"image_border_color\":\"#62363B\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":true},{\"id\":\"5ce1c39\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null,\"animation\":\"fadeInRight\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"8ae1467\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Idealizado e coordenado por Mirele Maravilhas (arte-educadora, cantora, brincante, produtora e terapeuta) e seu companheiro Guilherme Mar\\u00e1 (m\\u00fasico, arranjador, compositor e professor), o Cirandeira Cultural \\u00e9 desdobramento do N\\u00facleo de Pesquisa e Express\\u00e3o da Sanfona e 8 Baixos do Brasil que iniciou-se em 2013 pela necessidade de reconhecer, mapear e divulgar os tocadores da sanfona de 8 baixos (no qual Mar\\u00e1 \\u00e9 ex\\u00edmio tocador - disc\\u00edpulo do mestre Z\\u00e9 Calixto). De origem carioca, o casal, por conta de suas pesquisas, foram morar no sert\\u00e3o do cariri cearense, na cidade do Crato, Cear\\u00e1, ao p\\u00e9 da chapada do Araripe. Foram dois anos de muitas pesquisas, amizades e como resultado surgiu o projeto Sanfonada Brasileira, o\\u00a0 Encontro de Gera\\u00e7\\u00f5es e a oficina de musicaliza\\u00e7\\u00e3o a partir dos ritmos nordestinos.<\\/span><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0Depois do mergulho em terras Cariris no Sert\\u00e3o do Cear\\u00e1 e de passagens por Jo\\u00e3o Pessoa e pela Serra do Capara\\u00f3, o casal e sua filha, estabeleceram moradia na cidade serrana de Petr\\u00f3polis, Rio de Janeiro, desde 2017. Com o intuito de trazerem a cultura nordestina \\u00e0 cidade imperial, Mirele criou o grupo Arte de Brincantes, dedicados aos ritmos e dan\\u00e7as folcl\\u00f3ricas do norte\\/nordeste. Paralelamente, criou a Sanfonada Brasileira, que com apoio do SESC Quitandinha, realizou mais cinco edi\\u00e7\\u00f5es trazendo muita alegria e informa\\u00e7\\u00e3o ao p\\u00fablico petropolitano. Desse projeto, atrav\\u00e9s do mapeamento dos sanfoneiros da regi\\u00e3o, Guilherme Mar\\u00e1 idealizou e criou a Orquestra Sanf\\u00f4nica de Petr\\u00f3polis, que em um ano de vida, j\\u00e1 faz parte dos eventos da cidade.\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0Outros projetos tamb\\u00e9m foram surgindo, como \\u201cBrincando de Brincantes\\u201d - direcionado ao p\\u00fablico infantil, o \\u201cForrofiando uma hist\\u00f3ria\\u201d - apresenta\\u00e7\\u00e3o musical com conte\\u00fado did\\u00e1tico e o \\u201cFole e Folia\\u201d - uma jun\\u00e7\\u00e3o entre o Arte de Brincantes e a Orquestra Sanf\\u00f4nica de Petr\\u00f3polis e que atrav\\u00e9s de uma oficina de percuss\\u00e3o, formou-se um bloco de carnaval forrozeiro. O sucesso foi total, e muita alegria se espalhou pela cidade, no carnaval de 2020.<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"align\":\"center\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":true}],\"isInner\":true}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"50613f4\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"45\",\"right\":0,\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":0,\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"9ceaf69\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"9a6490f\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"Contato\",\"align\":\"center\",\"title_color\":\"#502025\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Russo One\",\"typography_font_size\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":45,\"sizes\":[]},\"typography_font_weight\":\"300\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"},{\"id\":\"1ecee3f\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"30\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"c114ae8\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":33,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"93fed91\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"bg_image\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/cirandeira.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020\\/10\\/blo-folia-e-arte.jpg\",\"id\":71},\"title\":\"Fole & Folia\",\"description\":\"\",\"button\":\"Confira\",\"link\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/cirandeira.com\\/folia-e-arte\\/\",\"is_external\":\"\",\"nofollow\":\"\",\"custom_attributes\":\"\"}},\"e